                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Confirmar exclusão</h3>
                    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600">Tem certeza que deseja excluir este empréstimo e suas parcelas?</p>
                    <div class="mt-6 flex items-center justify-end gap-3">
                        <button id="cancelDeleteLoanBtn" type="button" class="rounded-xl border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50">
                            Cancelar
                        </button>
                        <button id="confirmDeleteLoanBtn" type="button" class="rounded-xl bg-red-600 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-red-500">
                            Excluir
